  "title": "Optometrist (Clinic Specialist, 5.5 days)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Responsible for clinical evaluation of patients</li>\n  <li>Perform patients counselling on medical and surgical treatments</li>\n  <li>Handle diagnostics e.g HVF, OCT, Corneal Tomography, Biometry, Ultrasonography, Fundal and Anterior Segment Photography etc.</li>\n  <li>Support in laser refractive surgery (LASIK, RelexSMILE &amp; PRK)</li>\n</ul>\n<p>Requirements:</p>\n<ul>\n  <li><strong>OOB fully registered</strong></li>\n  <li>At least 2 years of experience as an <strong>Optometrist</strong></li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you are keen to apply for the position, kindly email your detailed resume in<strong> MS Word </strong>to <strong>hr@recruit-expert.com</strong></p>\n<p>Please note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p>\n<p>For more job opportunities, please visit our website at <a href=\"http://www.recruit-expert.com/\"><strong>www.recruit-expert.com</strong></a></p>\n<p>EA Licence: 19C9701</p>\n<p>Registration: R1326740</p>",
